President Cyril Ramaphosa will announce who is in his Cabinet on Wednesday at 20:00 from the Union Buildings in Pretoria. This was announced by the Presidency on Wednesday afternoon. Ramaphosa was inaugurated as president of the country on Saturday after the national and provincial elections were held earlier this month. https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/just-in-ramaphosa-to-unveil-his-cabinet-on-wednesday-evening-20190529